{"tid":269348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[六四嘉年華化] 快樂抗爭嘉年華　打鼓唱歌 high翻天 OL：咁嘅香港先似樣","createTime":"2017-06-03T16:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T17:08:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea1eb56d53f5d4adcd71a932c4e8b14e4bed1eca","tid":269348,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100109/13608947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100109%2F13608947&d=ul1OOknNQ2%2BL8WNHQg6mctZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=eb8a7b8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20100109%2F13608947&h=9c80b41c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20100109/13608947</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/09la2p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2F09la2p1.jpg&h=93a0b3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_d.gif&h=5f555858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紅紅藍藍的帳篷如花開遍名廈林立的中環，香港的商業中心昨天舉辦嘉年華；已經快要在這個城巿消失的舊日巿集、已經快要被「高速發展」所唾棄的社區經濟，在中環短暫復活一天。50後、60後、70後、80後，無分年齡先後，人人神態從容，展現對未來的盼望，對政府霸權拆村不再視而不顧，對不公義的小圈子選舉不再沉默。抗爭，要快樂，抗爭，要堅持到最後。黃昏下班的 OL走過，感慨說：「咁樣嘅香港先似番啲樣。」<br />\n記者：雷子樂、張嘉雯、張文傑、謝明明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_b.gif&h=993a51df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱鬧的議事堂外，氣溫低見14℃，溫熱的「不遷不拆鹹湯丸」、清香的「暖入心大地能量番薯糖水」、飽肚的「功能組別一舊飯」，連繫每個抗爭的巿民。有人全身髹上綠油，有人穿上鮮色太空衣，地上放着菜園模型、欄杆貼滿「沒有資格代表香港人」的功能組別議員照片。婦女們、年輕人個個埋頭苦幹，示威者萬眾一心，成就香港首個抗爭嘉年華。<br />\n<br />\n下午4時，財委會會議開始，場外的嘉年華正式展開，已解散的 indie樂隊「永遠懷念塔可夫斯基」揭開序幕，你打鼓，我唱歌，現場氣氛極為高漲，猶如台灣選舉的造勢晚會。抗爭者不時大喊「鄭汝樺大話精！」、「狗賊狗官！」、「歪理！」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20100109/large/A04_01_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100109%2Flarge%2FA04_01_a.gif&h=17b5563c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c200cb554987f7217b87e5daa7d4e14846522616","tid":269348,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"莊子的妻子死後，這位中國一代哲人打鼓唱歌，他對好奇的人解釋，他妻子自大自然而來，今回歸自然，自然可喜可賀，何哀傷之有。說得容易，聽得明白，但真正面對死亡，誰可豁達至此。那是自己的妻子，可不是淡如水的君子之交。<br />\n<br />\nHAPPY JAM返首歌賀六四<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20141128/photo/1128-00321-003v1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20141128%2Fphoto%2F1128-00321-003v1.jpg&h=642dab83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57a1f1b03712502b2ce82bf8240bdb405c5f85a9","tid":269348,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"經過雨傘佢地都係覺得今天我鳩坐係有用"},{"pid":"fec4e3618cd615691c1c2e3bb3903d1fae1b64f0","tid":269348,"uid":15410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經過雨傘佢地都係覺得今天我鳩坐係有用</blockquote><br />\n睇唔到條拎日期係2010?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7210ac13cd9a607056bc3f962b93b25855cb23","tid":269348,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"留名等樓下炒車"},{"pid":"41be0132d11d3631a3495311916c31e449ceaa5b","tid":269348,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等樓下炒車</blockquote><br />\n已經